Class LockedGate

java.lang.Object
edu.monash.fit2099.engine.GameEntity
edu.monash.fit2099.engine.positions.Ground
game.grounds.LockedGate
All Implemented Interfaces:
Printable, Resettable, Unlockable
public class LockedGate extends Ground implements Unlockable, Resettable
A subclass of Ground that implements Unlockable interface. A locked gate is a ground that can be unlocked by an unlock action, and allows an actor to travel to another map.

    • allowableActions

      public ActionList allowableActions(Actor actor, Location location, String direction)
      Returns an ActionList that contains the actions that can be performed on the gate. If the gate is locked, the ActionList contains an UnlockAction that allows an actor to unlock the gate with a key. If the gate is unlocked, the ActionList contains the travel action/actions that allows an actor to travel to another map through the gate. e
